divs: Sighting DetailsI walked out of my house in South Philadelphia to go to the corner store around the corner, as I walked out I looked up and saw the sun reflecting off a metalic disc shape object. I ran back in the house to grab my camera but by the time I got back outside the object was gone. To my amazement another cigar shape object was in sight this time. IT was incredible that after this one, there was one after another flying overhead. I've enclosed several pics of this cool event.
trends: There have been 216 other sightings in Philadelphia

Summary: cigar shape and disc shape objects flew over head one after another
